div.div:
travelDir (point):
x = 1 for east, -1 for west, 0 for north/south
y = 1 for south, -1 for north, 0 for east/west

div.style: display: inline-block; font-size: 10px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; vertical-align: top; width: 281px; white-space: nowrap; overflow-wrap: normal; text-align: center;

div.font:
if (steer dir is right and final dir is east or west) or
(steer dir is left and final dir is north or south):
y = travelDir.x * -1
x = travelDir.y * -1
else:
x = travelDir.y
y = travelDir.x
traveldir.x = x
travelDir.y = y
